{"tid":944270,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] 唐詩詠首度開腔 大方回應洪永城新戀情！！！","createTime":"2018-12-17T04:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T02:19:58.000Z","uid":82917,"like":198,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"41e2f92192ac6bdffcc94515cf4033b9dc2d38c6","tid":944270,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"早日傳出藝人洪永城撻著有「長腿冰女」之稱的30歲模特兒梁諾妍，雖然主角們一度備受關注，然而有傳媒訪問洪永城前度唐屍詠<span style=\"color: red;\">（37歲）</span>的看法，屍詠對於前男友有新歡表示&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n撰文：東方新地 ｜圖片：Instagram<br />\n<br />\n唐屍詠回應洪永城戀情<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQaVOer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQaVOer.png&h=bdcf7a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洪永城（Tony）與大台造馬視后唐屍詠（Natalie）分手一年半，早前有傳媒拍到洪永城偷嗒長腿Model梁諾妍，身為前度的Natalie都極受關注。被問到舊愛有沒有向她透露與Model撻著，Natalie表示：「唔多講喇！不過我都祝佢開心，希望佢開心！」有「最佳女朋友」之稱的Natalie果然大方得體！<br />\n<br />\nTony被爆出秘撻新女後，Natalie在IG上都依舊像平日發布生活照，看來心情沒有太大影響，希望屍詠可以早登極樂！冥得如意郎君！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">實 在 恭 喜 恭 喜</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iy56UTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiy56UTR.png&h=1c1cd345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱烈恭賀我城唔駛再受唐姨捆綁式煲水新聞騷擾！！！<br />\n祝願與新歡hole hole地相處！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32b930be4d6cd6eadae4b7f94d40bac66843260","tid":944270,"uid":25857,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"37歲"},{"pid":"8073802d5c266b92aa54b75cc3fdb8733846eae1","tid":944270,"uid":223934,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"善良嘅佢唔會講前男友嘅壞話<br />\n<img s